She smiled as Quickstrike put his arm around her. She whispered to 
him."Thank you commander."  
She walked back to her console and got the chair.  She brought it 
over to Quickstrike so he could sit down.  She said in a little 
louder voice, "As you commanded, your chair commander."
She held the chair for him, slightly smiling.
